{"tid":1398494,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣布，8月5日朝早一定要阻塞交通","createTime":"2019-08-02T21:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T20:37:14.000Z","uid":255194,"like":76,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c74e82b4cf1ba054542e6d00c40081c9a2ac75","tid":1398494,"uid":255194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T21:15:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>罷工</ins></span><br />\n係目前和理可以逼使政府回應既最後手段<br />\n<strong>但有幾多人星期一係攞唔到假</strong><br />\n或者係<strong>公司對罷工從未表過態？</strong><br />\n<strong>有幾多人驚因爲攞左假比公司秋後算帳？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以我地一定要幫佢地爭取<br />\n等佢地有理由同老細講返唔到工</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好再講失民意<br />\n要爭取既呢兩個月已經歸晒邊<br />\n罷工<strong><ins>人數</ins></strong>同<strong><ins>時間</ins></strong>都好重要<br />\n有第一次<br />\n先會有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第二次</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第三次</span><br />\n先可以達到影響經濟呢個目標<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以8月5日 一定要塞！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"dafbc6f20d42e72bf80925e6d8da94d98a8e579b","tid":1398494,"uid":196242,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T21:17:08.000Z","msg":"冇錯 同埋時間要比上次再早啲"},{"pid":"11937a609aa290649c1cf5806e51f4e94f0053a1","tid":1398494,"uid":179979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T23:31:19.000Z","msg":"眾籌同路人買防禦裝備，係裝備呀！！<br />\n安全帽口罩眼罩豬咀毛巾保鮮紙手套<br />\n基本物資都夠，講緊乜都有幾百以上<br />\n但裝備係完全唔夠呀！<br />\n同路人一齊眾籌防範裝備<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/G1kwjxBDBEMsTzgaz3S_Ow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FG1kwjxBDBEMsTzgaz3S_Ow&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDSK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=1c979492\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/G1kwjxBDBEMsTzgaz3S_Ow</a>"},{"pid":"53f582f69ea7439a788fdd4b6c43f867a17b4051","tid":1398494,"uid":267246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"